data.description: Transformed from its former self, this exquisitely revamped bungalow is a true masterpiece. Every corner of this residence has been meticulously reinvented with the most contemporary and upscale finishes. From stunning quartz countertops and pristine white cabinetry to luxurious vinyl plank flooring, elegant light fixtures, and a deep soaking tub, no detail has been spared. The property is graced with all-new windows, and so much more, making it a haven of sophistication.    A charming front porch extends a warm welcome to your new abode, while the house is nestled on an expansive, beautifully landscaped lot that offers ample space for the addition of a pool. Below, a fully finished basement unfolds, complete with a bedroom, a well-appointed bath, a convenient laundry room, and a walk-out patio, providing a versatile and functional living space.    Situated only minutes away from the Mercedes Benz Stadium, a vibrant array of restaurants, shopping outlets, and the scenic Browns Mill Golf Course, this property epitomizes the epitome of modern living and leisure.
